import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter,Route,Routes,Link} from "react-router-dom"
import App from "./App2"
import Temp from "./Temp"


function App3(){
    return (
        <>
            <BrowserRouter>
                <Link to="/temp">temp</Link>
                <Routes>
                    <Route path='/temp' component={Temp} />
                </Routes>

            </BrowserRouter>
        </>
    )
}

export default App3;
